# Mission plan

## Mission constraints (binding)

This mission is a **simplified** variant of [`.sedea/centers/research-and-development/missions/plan-and-deliver/plan.mdc`](.sedea/centers/research-and-development/missions/plan-and-deliver/plan.mdc). Unless a constraint below explicitly overrides plan-and-deliver, reuse that mission's skill procedures and **development-process.md** cadence.

| Constraint | Rule |
|------------|------|
| **PRD skill** | Always **`ad-hoc-prd`** ÔÇö never **`author-prd`**. |
| **Complexity ceiling** | Master Plan **`### Complexity score`** overall score must be **Ôëñ 20**. At **> 20** (ÔëÑ 21), stop and direct the developer to **`plan and deliver`** on **`plan-and-deliver`**. **20 is in band.** |
| **Phase model** | **One phase only** ÔÇö no multi-phase delivery tree. |
| **┬º6 decomposition** | Master Plan **always** uses **`PR breakdown`** ÔÇö never **`Delivery phases`**. |
| **Forbidden skills** | **`delivery-phases`**, **`phase-planner`** ÔÇö do not spawn or run inline on any lane. |
| **PR count cap** | **`pr-breakdown`** lists **1ÔÇô6** PR rows. **> 6** PRs or multi-initiative scope ÔåÆ use **`plan and deliver`**. |
| **Implementation / ship** | **`coding-session`** and detached ship chain unchanged ÔÇö same skills and gates as plan-and-deliver. |
| **Command phrase** | **`plan and deliver a single phase`** only (see **`mission.yaml`**). |

Skill paths reuse [`.sedea/centers/research-and-development/missions/plan-and-deliver/skills/`](.sedea/centers/research-and-development/missions/plan-and-deliver/skills/) unless this mission later adds mission-local copies.

